::Kluster::

Kluster grins, looking down at Hysteria. "We? We're going to meet a possible 
ally."

Phobia's ship was visible in front of them. Kluster quickens his pace, 
activating his comm-link.

"We're aproaching your ship," he says into it, "Me and two bots. Please do 
not be allarmed."
